# Base URL of the video-service API.
#   - Empty (default): same-origin; the Vite dev server proxies
#     /v1 and /healthz to http://localhost:8000.
#   - Production: set to the public API URL (e.g. https://api.example.com)
#     AND configure OH_CORS_ORIGINS on the backend to allow this origin.
VITE_API_BASE=
